parameters:
\N<Officer Luda>Are you all prepared? Tonight is a special banquet to
celebrate our victory. Everyone who isn't bedridden with
illness or lying down due to being in the final month of
pregnancy must attend the feast.

\N<Officer Luda>You should be grateful for Luda's mercy. Under normal
circumstances, it wouldn't be surprising if you were bound
and hanged.

\N<Officer Luda>As a wife for just one night, I'm giving you the opportunity
to serve as a comfort to our heroes.

\N<Officer Luda>Do your utmost to serve Luda's warriors and flatter them.
If you do, you may be able to prolong your life as a
concubine.
\N<Officer Luda>Now, it's time. Everyone move to the venue, hurry up.

\N<Officer Luda>What's wrong, what are you doing? Hurry to the banquet hall.
Especially you, since you're the center of everyone's
attention.

\N<Officer Luda>You'll work until you die... until you wither away. For
us... for Luda.
